ty may not be. High angular resolution\ninterferometers such as the Submillimeter Array (SMA) and ALMA may be able to\ndifferentiate between competing theories of gas giant planet formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2006 20:00:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
