ergoing quasistationary accretion, and a magnetic field collimated along the\nspin axis--a promising candidate for the central engine of a short gamma-ray\nburst. (Abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2006 20:33:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
